Trial protocol for the validation of the 'Toronto Aortic Stenosis Quality of 
Life (TASQ) Questionnaire' in patients undergoing surgical aortic valve 
replacement (SAVR) or transfemoral (TF) transcatheter aortic valve implantation 
(TAVI): the TASQ registry.

Frank D(1), Kennon S(2), Bonaros N(3), Romano M(4), Lefèvre T(4), Di Mario C(5), 
Stefàno P(5), Ribichini FL(6), Himbert D(7), Urena-Alcazar M(7), 
